{"article_id":"oHxA0i6lqM6doW6G","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Julie Swetnick , the third woman","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"to come forward with sexual misconduct allegations against Supreme Court nominee Judge Brett M. Kavanaugh ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"backed off some of those claims in a television interview","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that aired Tuesday night .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"NBC ,","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"which interviewed her ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"also said","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"none of the four people","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"she said","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"would corroborate her story","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"have done so .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Two didn ' t respond to the network ' s requests for comment ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"one had died","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and the fourth said","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"he didn ' t remember Ms. Swetnick","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"and didn ' t think","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"they socialized .","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"They also noted","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"her claims differed from the ones","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"made in her sworn affidavit","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"before airing the interview .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"In a sworn declaration last week Ms. Swetnick said","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh , as a high school student in the early 1980s , was \" present \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"when she was a victim of a \" train \" rape .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"She went further","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and claimed","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"to witness the two boys purposefully \" spiking \" drinks","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"to get girls drunk enough","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"for these rapes to occur .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"In the NBC interview , though , she said only","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"that she saw Judge Kavanaugh and a friend , Mark Judge ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"hanging around punch containers","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"and giving out cups to girls ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"but noted","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"she did not know","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"what he may have done .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"She also now says","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"she doesn ' t know","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"if he was part of the gang rape","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"she says","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"she suffered","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"- but she still suspects him .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"\" I can not specifically say","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"that he was one of the ones","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"that assaulted me , \"","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"she said ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"\" but earlier at that party , I saw Brett Kavanaugh there ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"I saw Mark Judge there . \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"When asked","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"if he was involved with the any alleged gang rapes ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Ms. Swetnick said","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"it was \" too coincidental \" to think otherwise .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh strongly denied Ms. Swetnick ' s allegations ,","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"calling them a \" joke \" and something from the \" Twilight Zone. \"","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"Mr. Judge has also denied the accusations .","depth":4},{"id":55,"text":"Reports have come forward","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"highlighting Ms. Swetnick ' s past with legal disputes ,","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"including a dismissed lawsuit from a former employer and a restraining order from her ex-husband","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"that was not approved .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"Both Ms. Swetnick and her lawyer Michael Avenatti ,","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"who also presents porn star Stormy Daniels ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"have dismissed the reports","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"and said","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"the lawsuits were a farce .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"Ms. Swetnick told NBC","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"she talked about the attack with her mother and with a Montgomery County police officer .","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"Both her mother and the officer","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"she named to NBC","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"are dead ,","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"and the network said","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"the county told her","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"it could take up to 30 days to respond to a request for any records .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"On Tuesday Ms. Swetnick ' s story faced more pushback","depth":3},{"id":73,"text":"- this time from a former friend","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"who contacted the Judiciary Committee of his own experience with Ms. Swetnick in the early 1990s .","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"He said in a letter to senators","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"that she picked him up at a bar ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"not caring","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"that he was married ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"and they grew close","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"- though stopped short of sex","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"after he learned of her fondness for \" sex with more than one guy at a time . \"","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"\" She first tried sex with multiple guys while in high school","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"and still liked it from time to time , \"","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Dennis Ketterer , the former friend , wrote .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"He broke things off ,","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"but in 1996 ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"running for Congress as a Democrat ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"he contacted her father","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"to try to reach her .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"Her father \" told me","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"that she had psychological and other problems . \"","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Mr. Ketterer , in the letter , said","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"he came forward now ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"knowing the pain","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"his admissions would have on his family ,","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"because he was so upset","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"by watching Judge Kavanagh ' s wife \" looking so sad \" at last week ' s hearing .","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"\" I felt","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that she needed to know","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"that in this instance , her husband was being mischaracterized , \"","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"he wrote .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Ms. Swetnick ' s lawyer , Michael Avenatti , called Mr. Ketterer ' s letter \" garbage . \"","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":205,"left":174,"right":204,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":174,"left":157,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":154,"right":156,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":123,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":106,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":104,"right":105,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":104,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":118,"right":121,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":112,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":108,"right":111,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":108,"left":107,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":107,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":110,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":110,"left":7,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":117,"left":11,"right":116,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"N